            <title>[CASSANDRA-5968] Nodetool info throws NPE when connected to a booting instance</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5968</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
